name: Blackstan's Bridge
description: It is my part 138/256 of nft256 first collab "Elon" (Elon Musk portrait made from unique 256 pieces from 256 artists) - you can find it selled to Ricky O'Donnell on fnd by searching nft256 tag. I called this piece "Blackstan's bridge". I made it with mixed 3d and paintover technique. I wish to make an animated version of this work. For now, i starting to sell it as it is.  Many of my future works will be about adventures of saint hero in hell. It is something about that. Story in hell begins...
